  <p>This is a simple Playlist app built using Express and Handlebars. I have posted 2 playlists in the app with songs that are part of my personal collection.</p>

<div class="ui segment">

  <h3>Contact</h3>
  <p><strong>Author:</strong> {{info.author}}</p>
